### Admin API - Collection of Full Parameter Requests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### 1. SÂN BAY (AIRPORTS)
### ============================================

### Get Airports - Full Parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/airports?airport_code=SGN&airport_name=Tan%20Son%20Nhat&city=Ho%20Chi%20Minh&airport_type=international&country_id=1&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Airports - Search by Code
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/airports?airport_code=SGN&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Airports - Search by City
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/airports?city=Ho%20Chi%20Minh&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Airports - International Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/airports?airport_type=international&country_id=1&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Airports - General Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/airports?search=SGN&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

